PrecisLeasing to the BRITISH COLUMBIA PAVILION CORPORATION, for a term of up to thirty (30) years, of a parcel of land situate at ABBOTSFORD AIRPORT which is to be used as a site for an exhibition pavilion to accommodate the Abbotsford Airshow Canada Association and other similar or incidental commercial activities associated or compatible with aviation.
